.TH WINWATCH 1
.SH NAME
winwatch \- monitor rio windows
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B winwatch
[
.B -f
.I font
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Winwatch
displays a list of
.IR rio (4)
windows as found in
.I /dev/wsys.
For each window a box containing the label of the window is displayed.
Right clicking a box unhides, raises and gives focus to the window.
The boxes are arranged in columns, new columns are created when
needed.  The listing is refreshed every 5 seconds.  Pressing `q' or
delete will make
.I winwatch
close itself.
.SH FILES
.B /dev/wsys/*/label
.SH SOURCE
.B /sys/src/cmd/winwatch.c
.SH SEE ALSO
.IR rio (1),
.IR window (1),
.IR rio (4).
